From af23b92323f94650b514ca2132766a7dbaf03e65 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "ryan.kuo" <ryan.kuo@realtek.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Feb 2023 18:36:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] [All][EasyMesh-DPP] Fix GAS initial req and resp
 advertisement protocol element based on spec.

[All][Easymesh-dpp] Process multi_ap in dpp chirp cmd to differentiate normal dpp and dpp_multi_ap.
